727893f-a.title: Queens: Rockaway Beach Boule - Beach 106th Street
727893f-a.text:
Rockaway Beach Boulevard, east from Beach 108th Street. At one time the Ocean Electric Railroad operated its lines on this Ave.
August 30, 1936.
P. L. Sperr.
Neg 8 Wo5
